title: How to Do Florida: Your Ultimate Florida Boat
text:
Updated: 5:47 p.m. Monday, Oct. 12, 2015 | Posted: 5:13 a.m. Monday, Oct. 12, 2015 How to Do Florida: Your Ultimate Florida Boat In Partnership with VisitFlorida.com 
How to Do Florida host Chad Crawford and boating experts show you a wide array of Florida boats that are ideal for all Florida boating, such as open water and offshore boating. Go streamlined and simple for a tighter budget. Or deck out the boat you need for some fancier fishing.
